---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home">
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Welcome to Macon Aero Modelers</h1>
    <p>Join us in the exciting world of radio-controlled model aviation</p>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">About Our Club</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        Macon Aero Modelers is a community of passionate model airplane enthusiasts. We welcome pilots of all skill levels, 
        from beginners to experienced flyers. Our club provides a safe and friendly environment to enjoy the hobby of 
        radio-controlled aviation.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        We meet regularly to fly, share knowledge, and enjoy the camaraderie of fellow model aviation enthusiasts. 
        Whether you're interested in sport flying, aerobatics, scale models, or FPV racing, you'll find like-minded 
        members at our club.
      </p>
      <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}new-members`} class="btn">Join Our Club</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">What We Offer</h2>
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem;">
      <div class="card">
        <h3 style="color: var(--primary-color); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Flying Field</h3>
        <p>Access to a well-maintained flying field with paved runways and ample space for all types of model aircraft.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 style="color: var(--primary-color); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Training Program</h3>
        <p>Comprehensive training for beginners with experienced instructors to help you learn to fly safely.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 style="color: var(--primary-color); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Events & Competitions</h3>
        <p>Regular fly-ins, competitions, and social events to connect with fellow enthusiasts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 style="color: var(--primary-color); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Community Support</h3>
        <p>A welcoming community ready to share knowledge, tips, and assistance with your models.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="text-align: center; background-color: var(--bg-light); padding: 3rem; border-radius: 8px;">
    <h2 class="section-title">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--text-light);">
      Whether you're new to the hobby or an experienced pilot, we'd love to have you join us.
    </p>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
      <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}new-members`} class="btn">Become a Member</a>
      <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}contact`} class="btn btn-secondary">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
